      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Andrea Manzo</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:222px;\"><a href=\"/File:AndreaManzo.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/c0/AndreaManzo.jpg/220px-AndreaManzo.jpg\" width=\"220\" height=\"220\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/c/c0/AndreaManzo.jpg 1.5x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:AndreaManzo.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Andrea Manzo <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Andrea Manzo</b>,<br />\nan Italian computer scientist and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Correspondence_chess\">correspondence chess</a> player,  IM of the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/International_Correspondence_Chess_Federation\">ICCF</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>.\nHe is author of the <a href=\"/Stockfish\" title=\"Stockfish\">Stockfish</a> derivative <a href=\"/ShashChess\" title=\"ShashChess\">ShashChess</a>, and co-author of <a href=\"/index.php?title=BrainLearn&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"BrainLearn (page does not exist)\">BrainLearn</a> based on <a href=\"/Brainfish\" title=\"Brainfish\">Brainfish</a>, and was member of the <a href=\"/Vitruvius\" title=\"Vitruvius\">Vitruvius</a> team around <a href=\"/Roberto_Munter\" title=\"Roberto Munter\">Roberto Munter</a>, as <a href=\"/Category:Opening_Book_Author\" title=\"Category:Opening Book Author\">book author</a> responsible for its <a href=\"/Opening_Book\" title=\"Opening Book\">opening book</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2018_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2018 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2020_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2020 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Andrea_Manzo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2018_...\">2018 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Andrea_Manzo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2018 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=68093\">ShashChess</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andrea Manzo</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 28, 2018</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=68120&amp;p=769919\">Build ShashChess for Android</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andrea Manzo</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 01, 2018</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=71754\">BrainLearn</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andrea Manzo</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 07, 2019</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2020_...\">2020 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Andrea_Manzo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2020 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/fishcooking/Wpk-9COzk64/ez643VTkAAAJ\">BrainLearn NNUE 1.0</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andrea Manzo</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">FishCooking</a>, July 25, 2020&#160;» <a href=\"/index.php?title=BrainLearn&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"BrainLearn (page does not exist)\">BrainLearn</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/fishcooking/yWtpz_FY5_Y/RMTG56fkAAAJ\">ShashChess NNUE 1.0</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andrea Manzo</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">FishCooking</a>, July 25, 2020&#160;» <a href=\"/ShashChess\" title=\"ShashChess\">ShashChess </a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=76539\">Request of help</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andrea Manzo</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 09, 2021</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=76632&amp;start=34\">Re: Interesting read about Fat Fritz 2</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andrea Manzo</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 20, 2021&#160;» <a href=\"/Fat_Fritz#Fat_Fritz_2\" title=\"Fat Fritz\">Fat Fritz 2</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/g/fishcooking/c/Iy1AlEZJWc8\">New BrainLearn and ShashChess</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andrea Manzo</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">FishCooking</a>, May 19, 2021</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Andrea_Manzo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/amchess\">amchess · GitHub</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.iccf.com/player?id=241224\">ICCF Player Details - IM Manzo, Andrea</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.vitruviuschess.com/About-Us.html\">VitruviusChess | About Us</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Andrea_Manzo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/amchess\">amchess · GitHub</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.iccf.com/player?id=241224\">ICCF Player Details - IM Manzo, Andrea</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.vitruviuschess.com/About-Us.html\">VitruviusChess | About Us</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301152454\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.016 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.018 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 65/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 138/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:7872-0!canonical and timestamp 20260301152454 and revision id 24905\n -->\n"
